Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:13.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,开始预选了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:08.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:11.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是是KID
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:17.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  一按开始的按钮 宝物箱就会出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:23.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也没注意这里是带短刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:27.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但还是只有KID在最初就甚至过了60级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哎  该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:34.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:40.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,即使在游戏厅 也是学习家呀  KID
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:44.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样 那可是非常重要的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:51.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,会出现两面墙的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:52.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,希望我能还给你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:01.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,给我把这个玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,赛车 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:10.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 拜托啦 硬币我出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哎只要是游戏  你都很擅长不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:15.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:19.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个  应该有什么都可以清除掉然后从新开始的隐藏技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,标记位啊   想看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:28.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么 好了 快点儿取得一个好名次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:40.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,现在我最想做的是能取得飞机大战的宝物 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:43.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 KID   -礼治君再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:45.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID不要跑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(156.8,29.867)}预选开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:04:01.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样说的话 KID没有弄到最前端位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:16.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你把我的收藏品拿哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,有眼力界儿就说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你这个小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:32.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 游戏什么的 给我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:40.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,感觉听谁说过就在这附近来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:44.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 干什么呢 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:44.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野 天哪  高野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这么乱呢  我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哦不 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,发型有点变了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,有点像人偶娃娃的感觉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了 怎么感觉你有点怪怪的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我不知道木户家在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对面是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:24.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然没告诉我你和高野住在一个小区呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:27.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没有隐藏着哟 只是碰巧在同一个住宅区而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,应该早点说的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:33.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你收留我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:35.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,撒娇也不可以  讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你们家真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这不是光速船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:46.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个不好意思 不要乱碰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:49.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,吉恩号真是帅呆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:52.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是究竟什么家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:55.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是超级战车呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:03.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 听到了吗 请不要乱碰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:08.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我会给弄好的 急什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,修好了 修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你们家真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我家不管买什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:17.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,都要开家庭会议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,正因为这样 我才决定让你收留我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:27.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  等一下 为什么你能玩飞机大战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吗  电视游戏机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:33.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这样就可以在家里电视上玩游戏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:41.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以无限的玩下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:44.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 与之前的电视游戏不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:49.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,只有放进光盘 就有各种各样的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个是划时代性的  任天堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:54.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 就不需要我家的游戏厅了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:00.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,游戏厅里面的游戏是游戏厅外面是没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:07.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这个借给我吧 就一周
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你就收留我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:11.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:24.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦 我把这个都带来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 无论如何 都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:30.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不行  你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明信  我要进来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有朋友在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:41.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的  那个  他是渡边礼治君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:50.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,18期没有 20 21也没有 23 24也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,到17 18都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:57.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  那个混蛋 把我收集重要的美女写真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这次的风营法修改之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在深夜营业时无法约束自身行为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:06.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊  可恶的风营法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:12.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(181.636,26.133)}风营法：1984年开始禁止游戏厅二十四小时营业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明信  有些事想和您说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 礼治 不用走的 在这里就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:37.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想成为我家的孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:44.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,话说 父亲  想说的话 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:50.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么  明信 是关于公司的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:55.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,超不多要在 ﾃﾞｭｯｾﾙﾄﾞﾙﾌ方面展开事业了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这几年一直在向这个方向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一起去德国生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,德国 是么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:08.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 在国外生活唉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:12.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在国外 明信还不知道的事情 有很多的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:16.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你以前很喜欢德国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:26.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:30.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我没有离开日本的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:31.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:35.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我有了想在日本做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:36.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:40.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,游戏   -游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:43.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,电视游戏的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,只要有电脑的话 哪里都可以玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个是家庭电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:53.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,而我所说的是 在游戏厅玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:55.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,游戏厅么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:58.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是那个深夜也不关门 聚集一些不良分子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没有道德观念可言的地方是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么没有道德啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:06.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你也差不多...  已经是晚上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:09.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你的家人可是在担心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:12.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没错 如果那么担心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,请把礼治送回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:45.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋 快点转弯啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你的家原来是游戏厅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:57.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 礼治 你这个混蛋  还知道回来啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,把我的三级书还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,, 啰嗦  有客人和我一起回来了  你就乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么客人 你这个混蛋 客人什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,客...你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  KID的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:14.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:18.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,, 在这里都是这么叫他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:22.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,  后面 请看后面  后面后面后面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明信  你还来这种地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:31.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 等下 喂    这种地方是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 这样很失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这么说很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:37.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:40.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 KID  还要玩给我们看哦  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:46.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID可是我们这有名的游戏玩家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID 用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊   这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一步没有白走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:12.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就会变快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊  以前都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,做什么呢   这里好厉害啊  过来过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:23.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:26.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:31.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,只是 在这里呢  把这个吃掉后就会喝回血的药
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊   还是不吃比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是KID
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,看这里  时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,过了五千之后箱子就会出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊   以前都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:45.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,红色的药水是杀龙的时候用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:50.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是在哪发现的啊..   这种秘技
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是KID  以前都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:56.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,给    -这个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID和同伴们的记录簿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:03.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为了通关游戏所必需的宝箱和攻略要点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,特别是为了通关 大家的合作是很必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:13.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 大家一起写在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是由他维系的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:21.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我啊   从他们那里也学了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这这里的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:24.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不会黑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,因为之前取到灯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  是取到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白么  -当然明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:34.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,向孩子学习  是么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的是让我吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被人反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:49.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,而且  还是第一次见到明信认真的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:53.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还真是傲慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:59.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那些臭小子 稍微不注意他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:00.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,又会胡闹任性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:05.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子 明明没什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是多余的担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,秀雄先生是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:18.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你 偶尔也和他认真的对决一次怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:19.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:25.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就是在这种时候  要用游戏来决胜负哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:30.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,虽然幽灵来了  但是不动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在做什么  这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:35.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  看啊  出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有些恐怖哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:41.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:45.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,能过来一下吗   -啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你的心意我已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:49.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,让我们用电视游戏来决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你要是赢了的话 就留在日本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:57.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我要是赢了的话 你就和我一起去德国生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就用那个游戏对决
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,赛 赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要认真比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:19.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,规则很简单  玩一次  分数高的人获胜 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:21.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就由我先来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:41.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,开始预选
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:56.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个好厉害  简直就像真的比赛一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:04.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事   和刚才完全不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:08.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 老爹动真格的话这是当然的  懂不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 废物老爸 打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:18.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:33.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:35.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:40.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不太擅长玩赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:46.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID你都不擅长 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:50.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID 去打抱不平吧 看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:55.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,Namco的袖珍本是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,超车了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:33.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这和开普通车 打方向盘的习惯是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:37.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这还是第一次看见这么高的得分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:40.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在高速路上跑300公里在世界上很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:43.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,300公里 那不是竞技之狼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,到明信你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:51.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,到明信你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个 拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,别输啊 KID
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:10.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你答应给我看最高分的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:15.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,预选准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在这里慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:37.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,然后 加速
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,转过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 向右打个大转
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,转弯处来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,再踩重点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:56.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在接下来了U型路处决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:09.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明白
