Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:15.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一口气握住方向盘 接着漂移 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:16.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:25.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID KID
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:32.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID KID
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:36.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:48.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不给我玩到第一名 KID
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:55.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:02.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这看上去可能更像是你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:03.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:06.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,因为时间是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,按照你喜欢的去做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:10.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我这样跟你妈妈说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:14.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吧 KID
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好的 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:23.86,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我也该告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:28.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 KID
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:29.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你哭了吗
