Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:52.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,大概正月回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:54.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:58.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我觉得他很帅 看他能不能在漂移一次看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不愧是父子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,都很擅长玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:12.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙 KID 刚刚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:17.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你的大门开了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:18.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,冲冲  -卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:30.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你现在有喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:35.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,据说恋爱能使女生变漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:42.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在正在被怀疑在IT业内
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:47.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,接受了巨额赃款的MARS公司门前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:49.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,担任MARS公司共同代表的木户
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,现在都还不见踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,据公司内部情报说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:56.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户在公司里非常的独立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:59.86,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,与旁边的职员基本都没都有交流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:07.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:12.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是木户
